                                            work in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/NRSU8GU6"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Uri1787Catalogus"/><title level="m">Bibliothecae Bodleianae codicum manuscriptorum orientalium, videlicet hebraicorum, chaldaicorum, syriacorum, aethiopicorum, arabicorum, persicorum, turcicorum, copticorumque, catalogus</title><author><forename>Joannes</forename><surname>Uri</surname></author><pubPlace>Oxonii</pubPlace><publisher>E Typographeo Clarendoniano</publisher><date>1787</date><biblScope unit="volume">I</biblScope><note type="url">http://digital.soas.ac.uk/LOADI10485/00001/4x</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Uri1787Catalogus</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Uri1787Catalogus</note><citedRange unit="page">28</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
